:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:3589:\"<p>Frontend Job Posting is an easy, lightweight add-on of <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/\">Simple Job Board</a> that enables frontend job post for a simple job board. Frontend users can create their profile by Signup/Login to their dashboard and can Add/Edit their jobs and manage the job applications from the frontend. It allows users to manage job features, job application fields, and resume of applicants.</p>\n<p><span class=\"label label-success\">New Features</span></p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li class=\"new-feature\">Added a math captcha for enhanced security and spam protection on the registration and login pages.</li>\n<li class=\"new-feature\">Enabled Job Packages as standalone products to display detailed information about each package.</li>\n<li>Added a checkbox option in Settings to enable or disable individual job package products.</li>\n<li>Updated the job package purchase process and made packages visible on the Employer Dashboard.</li>\n<li>Displayed the company name in the list of employers.</li>\n<li>Displayed employers\' first and last names in the list.</li>\n<li>Added a control to enable or disable automatic job approval at the user level.</li>\n<li>Integrated paid job listing feature powered by WooCommerce. Please visit the <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Paid-Job-Listing-Mannual.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">instruction guide</a> to configure this feature with your Job Board.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>Following is the list of shortcodes for the frontend job posting.</p>\n<p><strong>Shortcodes List</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>[frontend_jobpost] will show a form to add jobs from the frontend.</li>\n<li>[frontend_dashboard] will show the dashboard with settings &amp; resume manager.</li>\n<li>[frontend_signup] will show the Employer sign up form.</li>\n<li>[frontend_login] will show the Employer login page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>User Authentication</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>New User Registration/Login Page</li>\n<li>Admin would have to approve the user in order for it to become an employer.</li>\n<li>Whenever a user applies to become an employer it will be submitted as a draft and would require approval from the admin.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Employer Dashboard</strong><br />\nLogged in Employer can:</p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>Add/Edit/Delete/View Jobs</li>\n<li>Set default Jobs Features</li>\n<li>Set default Application Form Fields</li>\n<li>Can see the applicants list against their posted jobs.</li>\n<li>Post a new Job Page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>After creating a new job, an Employer can perform the following tasks:</p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>Add Job Title</li>\n<li>Add Job Features</li>\n<li>Add Job Application Form</li>\n<li>Select Job Category</li>\n<li>Select Job Location</li>\n<li>Select Job Type</li>\n<li>Add Company Details</li>\n<li>Company Name</li>\n<li>Company Logo</li>\n<li>Website Link</li>\n<li>Tagline</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Settings</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>Add settings tab for adding default</li>\n<li>Job Features</li>\n<li>Application Form Fields</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job is submitted as a “Pending Preview”. These need admin approval in order to get published.</p>\n<p><strong>Notifications</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"d-ul list2\">\n<li>Approve/Reject the registration request by the Employer.</li>\n<li>Send email notification upon approval/rejection to the employer.</li>\n<li>Approve/Reject the job post requested by the Employer.</li>\n<li>Send email notification upon approval/rejection of the job post requested by Employer.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:70:\"<p>This Add-on enables frontend job posting for Simple Job Board.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27203;i:1;i:27073;i:2;i:27489;i:3;i:28087;i:4;i:691;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:61153;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2023-07-05T13:35:16Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2023-07-05T13:35:21Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:100:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Frontend-Job-Posting-PaidListingAdd-on.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:38:\"Frontend-Job-Posting-PaidListingAdd-on\";s:3:\"alt\";s:49:\"Frontend Job Posting Add-on with Paid Job Listing\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;}}s:12:\"featured_src\";s:100:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Frontend-Job-Posting-PaidListingAdd-on.jpg\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"License\";s:4:\"slug\";s:7:\"license\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:9:\"variation\";b:1;s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:7:\"Regular\";i:1;s:8:\"Extended\";}}}s:9:\"downloads\";a:0:{}s:14:\"download_limit\";i:-1;s:15:\"download_expiry\";i:365;s:13:\"download_type\";s:8:\"standard\";s:13:\"purchase_note\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"total_sales\";i:262;s:10:\"variations\";a:2:{i:0;a:30:{s:2:\"id\";i:61452;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2023-09-05T09:10:36Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2026-05-04T19:18:03Z\";s:12:\"downloadable\";b:1;s:7:\"virtual\";b:1;s:9:\"permalink\";s:92:\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/frontend-jobposting-add-on/?attribute_license=Regular\";s:3:\"sku\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"price\";s:2:\"35\";s:13:\"regular_price\";s:2:\"39\";s:10:\"sale_price\";s:2:\"35\";s:7:\"taxable\";b:0;s:10:\"tax_status\";s:7:\"taxable\";s:9:\"tax_class\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"managing_stock\";b:0;s:14:\"stock_quantity\";N;s:8:\"in_stock\";b:1;s:18:\"backorders_allowed\";b:0;s:11:\"backordered\";b:0;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:7:\"on_sale\";b:1;s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{