gins/simple-job-board/\">Simple Job Board</a> plugin by allowing site admins/employers to add custom apply links to their job postings. With this add-on, employers can direct applicants to a specific URL or WhatsApp account where they can apply for the job, rather than using the default SJB application form.</p>\n<p>This custom apply link feature is especially useful for site admins/employers who have their own applicant tracking system or prefer to use a specific application form. It also provides a more personalized experience for applicants, as they can be directed to a custom landing page that reflects the employer\'s branding and provides more detailed information about the application process.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:146:\"<p>Redirect applicants to a specific URL or WhatsApp account where they can apply for the job, instead of using the default application form.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:774;i:1;i:27203;i:2;i:27489;i:3;i:157;i:4;i:691;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:59090;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2023-04-10T13:02:57Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2023-04-10T13:03:26Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/CustomApplyLinkBannerImage.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"CustomApplyLinkBannerImage\";s:3:\"alt\";s:37:\"Custom Apply Link Banner Image Add-on\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;}}s:12:\"featured_src\";s:88:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/CustomApplyLinkBannerImage.jpg\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"License\";s:4:\"slug\";s:7:\"license\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:9:\"variation\";b:1;s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:7:\"Regular\";i:1;s:8:\"Extended\";}}}s:9:\"downloads\";a:0:{}s:14:\"download_li