ss=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>35.00</bdi></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">&ndash;</span> <span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>99.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;35.00 through &#36;99.00</span>\";s:7:\"taxable\";b:0;s:10:\"tax_status\";s:7:\"taxable\";s:9:\"tax_class\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"managing_stock\";b:0;s:14:\"stock_quantity\";N;s:8:\"in_stock\";b:1;s:18:\"backorders_allowed\";b:0;s:11:\"backordered\";b:0;s:17:\"sold_individually\";b:1;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:8:\"featured\";b:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:18:\"catalog_visibility\";s:7:\"visible\";s:7:\"on_sale\";b:0;s:11:\"product_url\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1337:\"<p>Have you been looking for an add-on that helps you make a creative feel, style (typography, color, background color, icons color, border radius etc), job listing page, and job detail page with the WPBakery drag and drop? Job Board add-on for WPBakery is a very easy-to-install add-on by <a href=\"http://www.presstigers.com\">PressTigers</a> for <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/\">Simple Job Board</a> which allows you to style the job listing page &amp; job detail page with WPBakery.</p>\n<p>Please visit the <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Job-Board-Add-on-for-WPBakery-Usage-Guideline.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">instruction guide</a> to configure the WPBakery add-on with your Job Board and ensure you must have the WPBakery plugin installed on your website.<br />\nTo use the version 2.0 or higher, please refer to this <a href=\"https: