.presstigers.com/product/job-board-3-in-1-bundle/\";s:3:\"sku\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"price\";s:2:\"40\";s:13:\"regular_price\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"sale_price\";N;s:10:\"price_html\";s:419:\"<span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>40.00</bdi></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">&ndash;</span> <span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>119.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;40.00 through &#36;119.00</span>\";s:7:\"taxable\";b:0;s:10:\"tax_status\";s:7:\"taxable\";s:9:\"tax_class\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"managing_stock\";b:0;s:14:\"stock_quantity\";N;s:8:\"in_stock\";b:1;s:18:\"backorders_allowed\";b:0;s:11:\"backordered\";b:0;s:17:\"sold_individually\";b:1;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:8:\"featured\";b:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:18:\"catalog_visibility\";s:7:\"visible\";s:7:\"on_sale\";b:1;s:11:\"product_url\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1854:\"<p>Are you looking for a bundle of add-ons at a discount while purchasing multiple add-ons for the Simple Job Board?</p>\n<p>Yes, the wait is over! We are announcing our first bundle with top selling items. Job Board - 3 in 1 solution has the Email Attachment, Multiple Attachment Fields, and Job Expirator add-ons.</p>\n<p>Following are details of the bundle add-ons:</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/email-application-add-on/\">Email Attachment</a> add-on sends the uploaded resume of an applicant to Admin, HR &amp; Job Author via email. By using this add-on, you can get rid of the website login to receive the applicant’s request. You can also enable/disable receiving the applicant’s resume attachment through email using the global settings.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> <em><strong>If you are not getting emails then please install any SMTP plugin and configure it with your email account.</strong></em></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/multiple-attachment-fields-add-on/\">Multiple Attachment Fields</a> add-on adds a “file” field type in the job application form builder. You can add multiple file upload fields on the job application form via the dashboard. You can also set fields as optional or mandatory.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Note: It only supports the extensions (.pdf, .doc, .docx, .odt, .txt, .rtf) as per one Uploaded File settings.</strong></em></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-expirator-add-on/\">Job Expirator</a> add-on adds a Job Expirator meta box to your job posts at the backend. You can set the job expiry date for a job. The add-on automatically unpublished a job after its expiry period and it will be removed from the job listing. Additionally, you can also enable/disable this module against the individual job from its detail page.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:122:\"<p>Job Board &#8211; 3 in 1 solution has the Email Attachment, Multiple Attachment Fields, and Job Expirator add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27020;i:1;i:27407;i:2;i:4296;i:3;i:28489;i:4;i:774;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:27332;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2020-08-28T14:10:37Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2020-08-28T14:11:02Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:81:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Jobboard-3in1Bundle.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Jobboard-3in1Bundle\";s:3:\"al