u\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"price\";s:2:\"35\";s:13:\"regular_price\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"sale_price\";N;s:10:\"price_html\";s:419:\"<span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>35.00</bdi></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">&ndash;</span> <span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>109.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;35.00 through &#36;109.00</span>\";s:7:\"taxable\";b:0;s:10:\"tax_status\";s:7:\"taxable\";s:9:\"tax_class\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"managing_stock\";b:0;s:14:\"stock_quantity\";N;s:8:\"in_stock\";b:1;s:18:\"backorders_allowed\";b:0;s:11:\"backordered\";b:0;s:17:\"sold_individually\";b:1;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:8:\"featured\";b:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:18:\"catalog_visibility\";s:7:\"visible\";s:7:\"on_sale\";b:1;s:11:\"product_url\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1993:\"<p><strong>Are you looking for an all in one filter solution for your job board plugin?</strong></p>\n<p>Now, you can get them all in a bundle at a discounted price. We are announcing our <strong>All Filters</strong> bundle that contains all of our filter’s add-ons. All Filters Add-on Bundle includes Company Details &amp; Filter, Job Level Filter, Job Industry Filter, and Salary Range Filter add-ons.</p>\n<p>Following are details of the bundle add-ons:</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/company-filter-add-on/\">Company Details &amp; Filter</a> add-on provides company listing for Jobs and front-end filter. You can add companies, company tagline, company website, logo and company email from the dashboard. By using this add-on, you eliminate the need to add job data repeatedly. Just add the company details one time and then select the company for a job. You can also list specific company jobs by using the shortcode [jobpost company=\"company-slug\"] on page/post.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-level-filter-add-on/\">Job Level Filter</a> add-on adds a job level filter to your job filters. You can add job levels from the dashboard. By using this add-on, you can list jobs on the basis of job level by using the shortcode [jobpost level=\"job-level-slug\"] on page/post.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-industry-filter-add-on/\">Job Industry Filter</a> add-on adds a job industry filter to your job filters. You can add job industries from the dashboard. By using this add-on, you can list jobs on the basis of job industry by using the shortcode [jobpost industry=\"industry-slug\"] on page/post.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/salary-range-filter-add-on/\">Salary Range Filter</a> add-on adds a salary range filter to your job filter. You can add a salary filter from the dashboard. By using this add-on. You can also show and hide this filter according to your needs.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:144:\"<p>All filters add-on bundle includes Company Details &amp; Filter, Job Level Filter, Job Industry Filter, and Salary Range Filter add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27073;i:1;i:27407;i:2;i:114;i:3;i:104;i:4;i:459;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:32389;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-03-22T12:32:18Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2021-03-22T12:32:37Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:92:\"https://market.presstige