";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:2825:\"<p>PressTigers now brings you the Job Board - Applications Handling Bundle add-ons for its users!</p>\n<p>The application handling bundle contains 6 Add-ons i.e Job Application to PDF, Job Applications CSV Exporter, Job Application Deadline, Custom Job Application Statuses, Job Applications Counter, and Cloud Storage Connector add-ons.</p>\n<p>The best thing is, you can get all of them in a single purchase and at a discounted price.</p>\n<p>Following are details of the bundle add-ons:</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-application-to-pdf-add-on/\">Job Application to PDF</a> add-on adds a \"Print Application PDF\" link on the applicant listing &amp; detail page. This plugin utilizes the popular PDF library, TCPDF, to export applicant details as a PDF in your Job Board. By using this add-on, you can download a PDF application using just one click.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-applications-csv-exporter/\">Job Applications CSV Exporter</a> add-on downloads the details of all applicants against every job in the CSV file. You can also download the list with the details of all applications submitted between two dates i.e Start date and End date.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-application-deadline-add-on/\">Job Application Deadline</a> add-on adds a Job Deadline meta box to one\'s job posts at the backend. One can set a job deadline date for a job. It automatically shows the closed status for a job after its deadline period. Additionally, one can also enable/disable this module for an individual job from its detail page. This add-on is also compatible with Frontend Job Posting Add-on.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/custom-job-application-statuses-add-on/\">Custom Application Statuses</a> add-on gives you the liberty to define custom job application statuses. Once you’ve uploaded the add-on, you\'ll have the option to add news statuses, and furthermore alter the SJB default application statuses.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-applications-counter-add-on/\">Job Applications Counter</a> add-on extends the functionality of the Simple Job Board to display the ratio of the number of applications received by views. Once you\'ve uploaded the add-on, you\'ll be able to see Views, Applications, and Ratio columns in the \"Job Board\" &amp; \"All Job\" menu.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/cloud-storage-connector-add-on/\">Cloud Storage Connector</a> add-on lets you upload job attachments to Dropbox and Google Drive at the submission of applications. Once you\'ve installed the add-on, please configure your Dropbox and Google Drive connections from the setting and you\'ll be all set to upload files to your Dropbox and Google Drive.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:239:\"<p>Job Board &#8211; Applications Handling bundle has the Job Application to PDF, Job Applications CSV Exporter, Job Application Deadline, Custom Job Application Statuses, Job Applications Counter, and Cloud Storage Connector add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:157;i:1;i:132;i:2;i:27407;i:3;i:27489;i:4;i:774;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:41621;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-26T12:35:11Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-26T12:35:46Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:96:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-con