lly\";b:1;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:8:\"featured\";b:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:18:\"catalog_visibility\";s:7:\"visible\";s:7:\"on_sale\";b:1;s:11:\"product_url\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:2388:\"<p>PressTigers now brings you the 5 in 1 bundle add-ons for its users!</p>\n<p>The 5 in 1 bundle contains 5 Add-ons i.e Job Application to PDF Add-on, Job Application CSV Add-on, Category Based Hiring, Location Base hiring, and the Content Replacement Add-on.</p>\n<p>The best thing is, you can get all of them in a single purchase and at a discounted price.</p>\n<p>Following are details of the bundle add-ons:</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-application-to-pdf-add-on/\">Job Application to PDF</a> add-on adds a \"Print Application PDF\" link on the applicant listing &amp; detail page. This plugin utilizes the popular PDF library, TCPDF, to export applicant details as a PDF in your Job Board. By using this add-on, you can download a PDF application using just one click.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-applications-csv-exporter/\">Job Applications CSV Exporter</a> is an efficient and lightweight add-on that downloads the details of all applicants against every job in the CSV file. You can also download the list with the details of all applications submitted between two dates i.e Start date and End date.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/category-base-hiring/\">Category Base Hiring </a>add-on sends job notification to an HR added to each job category. You can also send an email to multiple HRs. This add-on is also compatible with Email Attachment for getting applicant resume and attachment via email. Click to buy <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/email-application-add-on/\">Email Attachment</a> add-on.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/location-base-hiring/\">Location Base Hiring</a> add-on sends job notification to an HR added to each job location. You can also send email to multiple HRs. This add-on is also compatible with Email Attachment for getting applicant resume and attachment via email. Click to buy <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/email-application-add-on/\">Email Attachment</a> add-on.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/content-replacement-add-on/\">Content Replacement</a> add-on changes the default placement of the Job Features section on the job detail page. You can display the \"Job Features\" section above the Job Description and add \"Job Description\" title to the Job Details section.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:171:\"<p>The 5 in 1 bundle contains Job Application to PDF, Job Applications CSV Exporter, Category Based Hiring, Location Base hiring, and the Content Replacement add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27020;i:1;i:27203;i:2;i:26056;i:3;i:11531;i:4;i:4296;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:27491;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2020-09-03T14:36:06Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2020-09-03T14:39:03Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:81:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Jobboard-5in1Bundle.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Jobboard-5in1Bundle\";s:3:\"alt\";s:36:\"Job board-5 in 1 Bundle Banner Image\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;}}s:12:\"featured_src\";s:81:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Jobboard-5in1Bundle.jpg\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Licens