:0;s:29:\"Job Applications CSV Exporter\";i:1;s:20:\"Category Base Hiring\";i:2;s:20:\"Location Base Hiring\";i:3;s:29:\"Job Application to PDF Add-on\";i:4;s:26:\"Content Replacement Add-On\";}}i:22;a:63:{s:5:\"title\";s:25:\"Job Board - 6 in 1 Bundle\";s:2:\"id\";i:41748;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-30T10:53:01Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2025-04-15T12:53:25Z\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"variable\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:12:\"downloadable\";b:0;s:7:\"virtual\";b:0;s:9:\"permalink\";s:63:\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-board-6-in-1-bundle/\";s:3:\"sku\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"price\";s:2:\"75\";s:13:\"regular_price\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"sale_price\";N;s:10:\"price_html\";s:419:\"<span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>75.00</bdi></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">&ndash;</span> <span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>229.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;75.00 through &#36;229.00</span>\";s:7:\"taxable\";b:0;s:10:\"tax_status\";s:7:\"taxable\";s:9:\"tax_class\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"managing_stock\";b:0;s:14:\"stock_quantity\";N;s:8:\"in_stock\";b:1;s:18:\"backorders_allowed\";b:0;s:11:\"backordered\";b:0;s:17:\"sold_individually\";b:1;s:12:\"purchaseable\";b:1;s:8:\"featured\";b:0;s:7:\"visible\";b:1;s:18:\"catalog_visibility\";s:7:\"visible\";s:7:\"on_sale\";b:1;s:11:\"product_url\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"button_text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:3237:\"<p>PressTigers now brings you the 6 in 1 bundle add-ons for its users!</p>\n<p>The 6 in 1 bundle contains 6 Add-ons i.e How to Apply, Featured Job Listing, Job Listings Import/Export, Job Board CAPTCHA, Bulk Resume Download, and Resume Preview add-ons.</p>\n<p>The best thing is, you can get all of them in a single purchase and at a discounted price.</p>\n<p>Following are details of the bundle add-ons:</p>\n<p>The<a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/how-to-apply-add-on/\"> How to Apply </a>is an efficient job application tool that controls the application submission mechanism. By using this add-on, one can set resume as required/optional. Additionally one can receive an applicant\'s resume directly to one\'s mailbox or according to given instructions.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/featured-job-listing-add-on/\">Featured Job Listing</a> add-on adds featured jobs at top of the listing. This plugin is focused on extensibility and ease of use. You can mark a job as featured from the dashboard. You can search feature jobs through search filters on the jobs listing page and archive jobs page.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-listings-import-export-add-on/\">Job Listings Import/Export</a> add-on that not only imports the jobs but also exports them into a CSV and an XML. You can also export jobs between two dates i.e Start date and End date, Job Categories, Job Locations, and Status.</p>\n<p><strong>Note: CSV File Must Be UTF-8 or UTF-8 Compatible</strong></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-board-captcha-add-on/\">Job Board CAPTCHA</a> is an effective security solution that adds google reCAPTCHA at the bottom of the job application form. This plugin utilizes the popular anti-spam library, Google reCAPTCHA, to help your Job Board stay clear of spam entries. By using this plugin, you can also set reCAPTCHA language from the Job Board reCAPTCHA Settings.</p>\n<p>Applicants are required to pass reCAPTCHA verification to confirm that they are not a robot before a job can be submitted.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:<em> Simple Job Board CAPTCHA add-on is only compatible with reCAPTCHA v2</em></strong></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/bulk-resume-download-add-on/\">Bulk Resume Download</a> add-on is a very easy-to-use add-on that allows you to download applicants\' resumes/attachments as a Zip file. It also adds the functionality to download the applicant resumes in bulk and/or you can download the resumes w.r.t your preferred dates i.e Start Date &amp; End Date. Another good thing about this addon is that it\'s also compatible with our Multiple Attachment Add-on.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/resume-preview-add-on/\">Resume Previewer</a> add-on enables a resume preview feature on the application page. It is also compatible with the <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/frontend-jobposting-add-on/\">Frontend Job Posting</a> add-on. You can also preview the resume by clicking the preview button on the frontend application listing page.</p>\n<p><strong>Note: <em>You can preview the resumes having extensions (.pdf, .doc, .docx, .odt, .rtf, .txt).</em></strong></p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:167:\"<p>The 6 in 1 bundle contains How to Apply, Featured Job Listing, Job Listings Import/Export, Job Board CAPTCHA, Bulk Resume Download, and Resume Preview add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:446;i:1;i:104;i:2;i:157;i:3;i:114;i:4;i:106;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:41749;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-30T10:23:27Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-30T10:23:46Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:81:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/JobBoard-6in1Bundle.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"JobBoard-6in1Bundle\";s:3:\"alt\";s:24:\"Job Board - 6 in1 Bun