ng_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:843:\"<p>Email Application Attachment is an add-on plugin for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board\">Simple Job Board</a></p>\n<p>Simple Job Board Email Attachment by <a href=\"http://www.presstigers.com\">PressTigers</a> is an easy and light weight add-on that sends the uploaded resume of an applicant to Admin, HR &amp; Job Author via email. This plugin is extendible and easy to use. You can directly receive the applicant\'s resume in your email. By using this add-on, you can get rid of the website login to receive the applicant\'s request. You can also enable/disable receiving the applicant\'s resume attachment through email using the global settings.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> <em><strong>If you are not getting emails then please install any SMTP plugin and configure it with your email account.</strong></em></p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:133:\"<p>Get complete applicant resume &amp; details in the email attachment and get rid of website login to retrieve the application.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"4.92\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:12;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:446;i:1;i:104;i:2;i:27407;i:3;i:683;i:4;i:133;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{i:0;s:6:\"Add-On\";i:1;s:5:\"email\";i:2;s:16:\"email-attachment\";i:3;s:11:\"paid-plugin\";i:4;s:16:\"simple job board\";}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:366;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2016-09-05T11:53:50Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2016-09-05T11:53:54Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:92:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/email-application-add-on-image.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Email Application Add-on Image\";s:3:\"alt\";s:30:\"Email Application Add-on Image\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;}}s:12:\"featured_src\";s:92:\"https://market.presstigers.com/w