\";s:6:\"weight\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1015:\"<p>How to Apply by <a href=\"http://presstigers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PressTigers</a> is an efficient job application tool that controls application submission mechanism. By using this add-on, one can set resume as required/optional. Additionally one can receive an applicant\'s resume directly to one\'s mailbox or according to given instructions.</p>\n<p>Using this plugin one can configure the application procedure for global jobs as well as individually against each job. One can configure the submission through instructions or remove/make optional resume upload.</p>\n<p><strong>New Feature!</strong><br />\nWe’re pleased to announce that LinkedIn is now integrated with our application form using this add-on. You can enable Apply with LinkedIn from Settings, allowing applicants to prefill their name and email automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:<em> Global application configurations are only applied on new job creations or when individual jobs are not configured.</em></strong></p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:80:\"<p>Configure job application submission mechanism with liberty as you want.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:8401;i:1;i:133;i:2;i:27404;i:3;i:27407;i:4;i:132;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{i:0;s:6:\"Add-On\";i:1;s:32:\"apply-through-instructions-notes\";i:2;s:15:\"job-application\";i:3;s:11:\"paid-plugin\";i:4;s:16:\"simple job board\";}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:460;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2016-10-05