";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1018:\"<p>Simple Job Board Search Box by <a href=\"http://www.presstigers.com\">PressTigers</a> is an easy and lightweight add-on that displays a search box with Keywords, Job Category, Job Type, and Job Location filters. On search, it will redirect to the Job Archive Page or the selected page as per settings configuration. You can add it by simply adding a shortcode <strong>[sjb_search]</strong> on the WP page/shortcode widget.</p>\n<p>It is also compatible with the<a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/company-filter-add-on/\"> Company Details and Filter</a>, <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-level-filter-add-on/\">Job Level Filter</a>, <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-industry-filter-add-on/\">Job Industry Filter</a>, and <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/salary-range-filter-add-on/\">Salary Range Filter</a> add-ons.</p>\n<p><span class=\"label label-success\">New Features</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added functionality to suggest keywords in search box.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:101:\"<p>Display search bar on any page/post/shortcode widget by inserting the [sjb_search] shortcode.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27203;i:1;i:27073;i:2;i:459;i:3;i:133;i:4;i:104;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:31788;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-02-19T12:07:24Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2021-02-19T12:07:47Z\";s:3:\"src\";s:75:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Job-SearchBox.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:21:\"Job Search Box Add-on\";s:3:\"alt\";s:21:\"Job Search Box Add-on\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;}}s:12:\"featured_src\";s:75:\"https://market.presstigers.com/wp-content/uploads