ob Industry Filter Add-on.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/google-job-search-and-indexing-api/\">Google Job Search &amp; Indexing API</a> add-on is responsible to integrate the Google Structured Data against each job so google can identify your jobs. It also does the instant indexing of the jobs on google, which means you can index your job URL instantly on google when you publish/update and remove a job.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/jobs-sorting-add-on/\">Jobs Sorting</a> add-on adds a sorting filter on the jobs listing page. It will sort the jobs based on job title, posted date, and job deadline date. This add-on is compatible with all job search filters and <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-application-deadline-add-on/\">Job Application Deadline</a> add-on. It will sort the jobs and both ascending and descending order.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://market.presstigers.com/product/job-search-box-add-on/\">Job Search Box</a> displays a search box with Keywords, Job Category, Job Type, and Job Location filters. On search, it will redirect to the Job Archive Page or the selected page as per settings configuration. You can add it by simply adding a shortcode <strong>[sjb_search]</strong> on the WP page/shortcode widget.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:151:\"<p>Job Board &#8211; Search and Sort bundle has the AJAX Job Search, Google Job Search and Indexing API, Jobs Sorting, and Job Search Box add-ons.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:157;i:1;i:27331;i:2;i:114;i:3;i:28087;i:4;i:8401;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:41618;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-26T11:43:12Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:20:\"2021-11-26T11:43:22Z\";s:3:\"src\