ht\";N;s:10:\"dimensions\";a:4:{s:6:\"length\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"in\";}s:17:\"shipping_required\";b:1;s:16:\"shipping_taxable\";b:1;s:14:\"shipping_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"shipping_class_id\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:1003:\"<p>Content Replacement is an add-on plugin for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board\">Simple Job Board</a></p>\n<p>Simple Job Board Content Replacement by <a href=\"http://www.presstigers.com\">PressTigers</a> is an easy and light weight add-on that changes the default placement of the Job Features section on the job detail page.This plugin is extendible and easy to use. By using this add-on, you can display the \"Job Features\" section above the Job Description and add \"Job Description\" title to the Job Description section.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> In our add-ons (version 2.0.0 or later) for <a href=\"/product/job-board-add-on-for-wpbakery/\">WPBakery</a>, <a href=\"/product/job-board-add-on-for-divi-builder/\">Divi</a>, and <a href=\"/product/job-board-add-on-for-elementor/\">Elementor</a>, we’ve introduced options to place job meta, features, and the application form wherever you need on individual job posts. In this case, you may not require this add-on.</p>\n\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:123:\"<p>Add Job Description title to Description &amp; swap placement of job description section with job features section.</p>\n\";s:15:\"reviews_allowed\";b:1;s:14:\"average_rating\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:12:\"rating_count\";i:0;s:11:\"related_ids\";a:5:{i:0;i:27407;i:1;i:106;i:2;i:683;i:3;i:459;i:4;i:28518;}s:10:\"upsell_ids\";a:0:{}s:14:\"cross_sell_ids\";a:0:{}s:9:\"parent_id\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"Simple Job Board\";}s:4:\"tags\";a:4:{i:0;s:6:\"Add-On\";i:1;s:7:\"Content\";i:2;s:11:\"paid-plugin\";i:3;s:16:\"simple job board\";}s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:2:\"id\";i:364;s:10:\"created_at\";s:20:\"2016-09-05T11:52:25Z\";s:10:\"updated_at\";