(17219, 541, 'more_details_p_1', 'Caguar is a unified operations platform that provides real-time control over municipal fleets, waste collection systems, and field workforce activities. It combines GPS tracking, RFID verification, and intelligent routing with predictive insights to improve efficiency, transparency, and accountability in city operations.'),
