(22001, 928, 'hero_section_short_description', 'LESYS delivers technology-enabled cleaning operations that integrate workforce management, digital inspections, IoT-enabled monitoring, and performance analytics to improve cleanliness standards and operational efficiency across cities, facilities, and public environments.'),
